{"tid":31359,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"［轉］神舟11月末外匯儲備環比減少691億美元 1月以來最大單月降幅","createTime":"2016-12-09T15:37:07.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-10T08:17:00.000Z","uid":28016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8dbfec93f2e5bd22a40a81c5f11aca4b42a381bb","tid":31359,"uid":28016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T15:37:07.000Z","msg":"國際在線消息（記者 徐艷清）：神州人民銀行公佈的最新外匯儲備規模數據顯示，１１月末，神州外匯儲備規模較１０月底下降６９１億美元，報３．０５萬億美元。這是今年１月以來最大單月降幅，且為連續第五個月下滑。<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;國家外匯管理局分析稱，從１１月份的情況看，神州央行向市場提供外匯資金以調節外匯供需平衡、美國大選後非美元貨幣對美元匯率總體呈現貶值、債券價格也出現回調等多重因素綜合作用，導致外匯儲備規模出現下降。"},{"pid":"0f9f6a1def6ca449bc2c7681b1b4a78e38524a3b","tid":31359,"uid":28016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T15:37:40.000Z","msg":"Source: <a href=\"https://www.tuo8.club/forum.php?mod=viewthread&amp;tid=107664&amp;extra=page%3D1&amp;mobile=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tuo8.club%2Fforum.php%3Fmod%3Dviewthread%26tid%3D107664%26extra%3Dpage%253D1%26mobile%3D2&d=IFSoehw9b4HQe4nYzidLpYscwJTI%2BQouKF8MUrnyvY0%3D&h=4db502e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.tuo8.club/forum.php?mod=viewthread&amp;tid=107664&amp;extra=page%3D1&amp;mobile=2</a>"},{"pid":"c1f47238f7999e5f7c0165c8015a74c319fe2a57","tid":31359,"uid":28016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T15:43:22.000Z","msg":"11月4千幾億美元順差，外儲反而下跌691億美元，走得快好世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b0337fa9ec92506ff8fc1b256d0caae20cb351a","tid":31359,"uid":59839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T15:44:37.000Z","msg":"12月係唔係可以穿3萬億<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6ccfffa3c6d39a8e492c0dc8c6fa317be98280d","tid":31359,"uid":28016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T16:22:03.000Z","